党员领导干部法纪意识，提升法治能力。坚持以人民为中心，推动信访工作法治化，引导广大党员群众依法依规反映问题、表达诉求。进一步加强执法司法规范化建设，努力让人民群众在每一个司法案件中都能感受到公平正义。（河北日报客户端）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-46dc2219debb586a2ebfb63299f341bf_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/652409151"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIj6metKK+tJh3EAMaCTEwNzI1NzM2NSCJ8tSwBjAAOLcEQC9yCTY1MjQwOTE1MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1712736732.501498", "card_id": "Q_652294237", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "科研工作者该如何平衡科研和生活？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "对年轻人而言，很显然二者不可得兼，但依然不死心，试问天下科研工作同行前辈朋友们，是否有兼顾科研与生活的巧妙办法。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-5f517de1fe372fe04043304c636a9288_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/652294237"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ij6metKK+tJh3EAMaCTEwNzIzMTgzMiCCoNCwBjAAOElAMHIJNjUyMjk0MjM3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1712736732.502002", "card_id": "Q_645530974", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些毛骨悚然的恐怖故事？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-df9298b2792b8f03eb529446024738b7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/645530974"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ij6metKK+tJh3EAMaCTEwNTcyODk0OSCA9uCuBjAAODdAMXIJNjQ1NTMwOTc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true